{"id":576469,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/01/【立此存照】同性恋分子又来搞事/","date":"2018-01-13T09:13:30Z","modified":"2018-01-13T13:42:09Z","title":"【立此存照】“同性恋分子又来搞事”","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>随着罗茜茜实名举报北航陈小武性骚扰的事件发展，中国各地高校也开始有学生组织发表联署公开信，大量学生实名呼吁学校建立长效反性骚扰机制。这些发表在社交网站上的公开信大多都遭到了删除。广东外语外贸大学校友为联名信征集签名的过程，也算是集中表现了几个各方施压的常见手段。</p>\n<p><strong>1. 指发起者“搞事”或勾结境外势力</strong>（后者更为常见）：</p>\n<blockquote><p>@鱼里鱼闯江湖：[哈哈][哈哈]校友呼吁校园反性骚扰，被@广东外语外贸大学 辅导员说成：同性恋分子又来搞事！！<br />\n校友：我是诚心诚意地希望母校能更好，怎么变成搞事的……<br />\n同/异/X性恋分子的朋友可点击以下链接，或扫二维码参与联署支持 <a href=\"https://f.lingxi360.com/f?fid=sBvOL3wdUViTW&amp;utm_bccid=LXE6qZM6Vd0z\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">网页链接</a><br />\n#校园反性骚扰##metoo在中国# @女权之声 ​​​​</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/006bC7SGly1fndpd4monfj30f80j3tai.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-576471\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/006bC7SGly1fndpd4monfj30f80j3tai.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"564\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/006bC7SGly1fndpd4monfj30f80j3tai.jpg 548w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/006bC7SGly1fndpd4monfj30f80j3tai-239x300.jpg 239w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/006bC7SGly1fndpd49hcsj30hr0ba763.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-576472\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/006bC7SGly1fndpd49hcsj30hr0ba763.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"318\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/006bC7SGly1fndpd49hcsj30hr0ba763.jpg 639w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/006bC7SGly1fndpd49hcsj30hr0ba763-300x191.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>2. 删公开信：</strong></p>\n<p>发布《广外校友实名要求建立校园性骚扰防治机制的公开信》的微信公号“我爱广外”的近况是这样的：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_576470\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/广外.jpeg\"><img class=\"wp-image-576470\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/广外.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"627\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/广外.jpeg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/广外-191x300.jpeg 191w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">“我爱广外”微信公号页面截图</span></p></div>\n<p>与公开信相关的两篇文章均因“违规”被删。</p>\n<p><strong>3. 中止签名征集</strong></p>\n<p>广外校友公开信签名收集页面些现实已停止收集：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/广外2.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-576475\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/广外2.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"627\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/广外2.jpeg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/广外2-191x300.jpeg 191w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>附：《广外校友实名要求建立校园性骚扰防治机制的公开信》全文</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/006bC7SGly1fndpd5ehgfj30qo3bdqmz.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-576473\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/006bC7SGly1fndpd5ehgfj30qo3bdqmz.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"2461\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/006bC7SGly1fndpd5ehgfj30qo3bdqmz.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/006bC7SGly1fndpd5ehgfj30qo3bdqmz-67x300.jpg 67w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/006bC7SGly1fndpd5ehgfj30qo3bdqmz-229x1024.jpg 229w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[33760,33747,26991,27113,18979,29781]}